\s RIRIMBA MUGENI WAKUNZWE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ririmba Mugeni wakunzwe ugir’uj’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ahabona, Umukwe wanse guhemukira ng’uyo \bd*\bd Araje\bd*\bd ; ivy’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ucamwo n’ivy’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ubona ntibikaguc’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd intege, raba kw’isaha usanga igihe kigeze kure.\bd*
\pc \bdit Haleluya Mana yanje n’\bdit*\bdit U\bdit*\bdit shimwe, watoy’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit Umugeni mu mahanga nshima ko ndimwo, Haleluya Mana nzogutazira, nkiri mur’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ino si nzoririmba \bdit*\bdit Urukundo \bdit*\bdit rwawe.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Es’ukuntu Yerusalemu waka nk’izuba, kubw’\bd*\bd  Amasezerano \bd*\bd dufise tuzowubamwo; es’ukuntu Yesu wamaze kwambika Umugeni, urahiriwe we watorewe gutah’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ubwo \bd*\bd Bukwe\bd*\bd .\bd*
\pc \bdit Haleluya Mana yanje n’Ushimwe, watoy’ Umugeni mu mahanga nshima ko ndimwo, Haleluya Mana nzogutazira, nkiri mur’ ino si nzoririmba Urukundo rwawe.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Agakiza kawe kari hafi ewe Mugeni, imibabar’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ubabarizwa mw’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd iy’isi igira ishire; Yesu \bd*\bd Shimwa \bd*\bd we watoye Umugeni mu mahanga, ndizeye yukw’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Ishengero ryawe riri mu gutaha.\bd*
\pc \bdit Haleluya Mana yanje n’Ushimwe, watoy’ Umugeni mu mahanga nshima ko ndimwo, Haleluya Mana nzogutazira, nkiri mur’ ino si nzoririmba Urukundo rwawe.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ikizobemeza yuko mwatorewe ubwo Bukwe, muzogiriranir’\bd*\bd  Urukundo \bd*\bd abantu batangare; nsabiye \bd*\bd Ishengero \bd*\bd ryose kugira urwo rukundo, teg’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd utwi iryo sengesho Yesu rigushikire. \bd*
\pc \bdit Haleluya Mana yanje n’Ushimwe, watoy’ Umugeni mu mahanga nshima ko ndimwo, Haleluya Mana nzogutazira, nkiri mur’ ino si nzoririmba Urukundo rwawe.\bdit*\bd  \bd*
